very different than yours: all this extra energy I have. I've been a rebel of some sorts since childhood but growing body + emotions with a healthy dose of hormones all going in a totally different direction = Ping Pong Face! I remember mentioning it to one of my family members years ago - I'm like "I'm angry, depressed, sad, flustered, I'm bouncing off the walls, I'm an axe murderer, I'm a space alien etc - WHAT IS GOING ON!?"

Today, I've got 3 steps:

- I'm very careful about how I move now (I don't know what I would do without my yoga + stretching classes - wish they would do once a day everyday)

- I snack on fruits/green tea/kefir all day versus any kind of sweets/take away

- I've started taking fish oil

I'll be thinking about you!
